domain.locations

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.locations.Location
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Control, Hallway01, Hallway02, Laser, Mainhall01, Mainhall02, Net, Outside, Oxygen, Personal, Scanning

    public abstract class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    This is used to group together a series of Rooms, and is only created once in the LocationsController.createLocations().

    Within the Location is the rooms and exits stored which are filled upon creation (createLocation()).
